{"tid":279563,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲可以送動畫faker 比我？","createTime":"2017-06-11T11:17:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-11T11:42:19.000Z","uid":53553,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3877172726e83f4a1f446c4652cfd2565e567975","tid":279563,"uid":53553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T11:17:53.000Z","msg":"利申左先 屋企冇乜錢買Fake架<br />\n唔係話窮到穿窿 但就算有多餘錢都唔係去買fake架<br />\n<br />\n我下年想學睇動畫  睇動畫買個pvc百幾蚊好似唔太貴 <br />\n但屋企唔太多錢 百幾蚊食到一個星期了 <br />\n<br />\n所以睇下有冇巴絲有d全新/新淨ge二手figure讓出黎 <br />\n送比我就當然最好 但如果係平平地放比我我都唔介意嫁 <br />\n希望各位巴絲幫幫忙 如果有野想交換可以問下我 <br />\n<br />\n祝各位暑假快樂 今年願望除左共匪倒台之外 <br />\n其中一個細細地ge願望就係想自己有個動畫figure<br />\n同識班動畫迷 等自己生活冇咁頹廢"},{"pid":"585879d5d22f2e547871970523d4d54c8fc8583e","tid":279563,"uid":53553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T11:18:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef20c22e5f8074db41c00abdcdf3990ff2a0903","tid":279563,"uid":22820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T11:19:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aebd5f75d0ebaf95a2490c5baa939bbfde376627","tid":279563,"uid":53553,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T11:20:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n留粒膠就算？"},{"pid":"e81695229bacc2a7aca2f46ad279d525d10ce1a7","tid":279563,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T11:21:49.000Z","msg":"有個用咗幾年嘅焗爐"},{"pid":"d1ffff0cffa34a6c7dabd61da104d6a8a0f85ae6","tid":279563,"uid":53553,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T11:22:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有個用咗幾年嘅焗爐</blockquote><br />\nFaker阿 唔識中文？"},{"pid":"7f0ff276a461f89b66ba0e8e0cbca150d8ecec1a","tid":279563,"uid":22820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T11:29:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote